Integer ~ 2 * 10^9
Long ~ 9 * 10^18

Consider for overflows in the calculations:
mid = left + (right-left)/2;

For Arrays questions:
1. Visualize using continuous histogram

When a sorted array is given things that must come to mind:
1. Binary Search
2. Two pointer technique -> Three Sum, Container with most water.

Consider using max & min functions.


Best Trick:
Meditate before the interview. :)